---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <Header />

  <main class="py-8">
    <HeroSection 
      title="About Us" 
      description="Choose a plan that fits your mission. All options include a 14-day free trial—no credit card required."
    />

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-secondary-500">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-24">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-accent-500 text-secondary-600 dark:text-white font-medium text-sm mb-4">
              Our Story
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">From Startup to Industry Leader</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Green Orbit Digital was founded on a shared belief: space holds the key to solving some of the world’s most pressing challenges. We are a sustainable marketing agency dedicated to helping businesses communicate complex, space-enabled solutions through clear, impactful strategies that drive meaningful change.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Our journey has had its challenges, but our commitment to innovation, quality, and client success remains steadfast. Today, we proudly stand as a recognised leader in the sustainable SaaS marketing space, empowering organisations to transform their operations and achieve measurable impact.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              As we grow, we stay true to our core mission: equipping businesses with the tools they need to thrive responsibly in the digital era.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80" 
              alt="Team Collaboration" 
              class="w-full h-auto" 
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section relative z-10 overflow-hidden py-12 md:py-16">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-accent-500 text-secondary-600 dark:text-white font-medium text-sm mb-4">
            Our Values
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-6 gap-y-12">

          <!-- Card: Innovation -->
          <div class="feature-card group perspective">
            <div class="relative h-full min-h-[380px] w-full transform-gpu transition-transform duration-700 preserve-3d group-hover:rotate-y-180">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 dark:bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Innovation</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">The fuel for progress.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden rotate-y-180">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full bg-primary-600 dark:bg-accent-500 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Innovation</h3>
                  <p class="mb-4">
                    Creativity and innovation drive transformation. We push boundaries, crafting sustainable marketing strategies that empower businesses to thrive responsibly. Innovation lies at our core—developing new solutions, tackling challenges, and championing positive change within the space sector and beyond.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card: Responsibility -->
          <div class="feature-card group perspective">
            <div class="relative h-full min-h-[380px] w-full transform-gpu transition-transform duration-700 preserve-3d group-hover:rotate-y-180">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 dark:bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Responsibility</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Ethical leadership in action.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden rotate-y-180">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full bg-primary-600 dark:bg-accent-500 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Responsibility</h3>
                  <p class="mb-4">
                    With great power comes great responsibility. We champion responsible practices across the space, smart cities, and maritime sectors. Our stewardship extends to clients, communities, and the environment, ensuring ethical leadership guides all our actions.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card: Collaboration -->
          <div class="feature-card group perspective">
            <div class="relative h-full min-h-[380px] w-full transform-gpu transition-transform duration-700 preserve-3d group-hover:rotate-y-180">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 dark:bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Collaboration</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Strength in unity.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden rotate-y-180">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full bg-primary-600 dark:bg-accent-500 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Collaboration</h3>
                  <p class="mb-4">
                    The best outcomes arise from collaboration. We value diverse perspectives and work closely with clients, partners, and our team to craft marketing strategies that deliver business results while advancing societal and environmental impact.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card: Impact -->
          <div class="feature-card group perspective">
            <div class="relative h-full min-h-[380px] w-full transform-gpu transition-transform duration-700 preserve-3d group-hover:rotate-y-180">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 dark:bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Impact</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Purpose-driven success.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden rotate-y-180">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full bg-primary-600 dark:bg-accent-500 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Impact</h3>
                  <p class="mb-4">
                    We measure success by the positive impact we create. From enhancing space operations to supporting smart cities, our campaigns focus on building a sustainable, prosperous, and equitable future.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card: Integrity -->
          <div class="feature-card group perspective">
            <div class="relative h-full min-h-[380px] w-full transform-gpu transition-transform duration-700 preserve-3d group-hover:rotate-y-180">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 dark:bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Integrity</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Honesty in every step.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden rotate-y-180">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full bg-primary-600 dark:bg-accent-500 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Integrity</h3>
                  <p class="mb-4">
                    Trust is foundational. We uphold the highest ethical standards with transparency and accountability, ensuring clients and partners can rely on our commitment to their success and sustainability.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card: Continuous Improvement -->
          <div class="feature-card group perspective">
            <div class="relative h-full min-h-[380px] w-full transform-gpu transition-transform duration-700 preserve-3d group-hover:rotate-y-180">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl bg-primary-100 dark:bg-accent-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Continuous Improvement</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Evolving for a better tomorrow.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 backface-hidden rotate-y-180">
                <div class="card p-6 md:p-8 h-full bg-primary-600 dark:bg-accent-500 text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Continuous Improvement</h3>
                  <p class="mb-4">
                    We embrace a culture of continuous learning and adaptation. Staying at the forefront of sustainable marketing, we deliver innovative solutions tailored to the evolving needs of the space industry and beyond.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
<section class="section relative z-10 overflow-hidden py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="container-custom max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-100 dark:bg-accent-500 text-secondary-600 dark:text-white font-medium text-sm mb-4">
